About Mysha Properties

Founded by Sulthan Sait in February 2025.
Cutting through the complexity of investment and delivering results.

What we do: Off-plan deals. Ready-to-move-in properties. Land transactions. Property management. Strategic portfolio building that actually makes sense.
Our main goal is to bring in new investors from India, Russia, China, Europe, and the British Peninsula who are smart enough to see Dubai's opportunity but need a straight-shooting guide to capture it.

No fluff. No runaround. Just clear advice, handpicked opportunities, and end-to-end execution.
Your Dubai investment starts here.
